&lt;p&gt;This individual will provide statistical expertise across Prime’s clinical portfolio, including input on study design, protocol development, dose-escalation strategy, interim analyses, regulatory interactions, and submission planning. In parallel, the individual will build and lead an integrated Biometrics function by providing strategic oversight and line management of Clinical Data Management while partnering closely with Clinical Development, Clinical Operations, Regulatory Affairs, Medical Writing, Translational Medicine and other functions.&lt;/p&gt;
