&lt;li&gt;Provide overall biometrics leadership across Prime Medicine’s clinical programs, spanning:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Biostatistics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data Management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Statistical programming (via vendors)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and implement biometrics strategies appropriate for early- and mid-stage gene therapy development, including:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Study design and statistical approaches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Endpoint selection and estimands&lt;/li&gt;
